    <title>Modify gerrit's username (NoteDB)</title>
    <url>/2019/09/02/Modify-gerrit-username/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p><a href="https://blog.3skel.com/2019/03/gerrit-converting-from-http-auth-to-ldap/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://blog.3skel.com/2019/03/gerrit-converting-from-http-auth-to-ldap/</a></p>
<p>git clone “ssh://gerrit/All-Users”<br>git fetch origin refs/meta/external-ids<br>git checkout -b extid FETCH_HEAD</p>
